      <title>预算出台前，莫迪祈求财富女神保佑中产阶级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/ahead-of-budget-modi-asks-wealth-goddess-to-bless-middle-class</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪周五援引印度教财富女神的话语来提升印度穷人和中产阶级的地位，这可能预示着政府可能会在第二天的预算中推出措施来提振疲软的消费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/ahead-of-budget-modi-asks-wealth-goddess-to-bless-middle-class</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 06:11:43 GMT</pubDate>
